comments: Unusual? Everything, it didn't make sense, even the images were weird, Alien stuff I guess. To identify the images names as fast as possible I tried to remember only the center part of the name, which was that one richer of features. Surely the second task was hard, not because I didn't remember but because you asked me to look at the center while the entire name was often shifted to the left, or the right, which made the task quite hard to me. Study was interesting by the way, keep this up.
